reviewText: Mel Gibson may be getting some bad press these days but "Bird on a Wire" reminds us of why he was once one of Hollywood's biggest stars. Mel is his cute, hot and engaging self here and he's perfectly matched with the charmingly neurotic Goldie Hawn as his love interest. This movie is a great mix of action and comedy - perfect for date night.As for the "Cowboy Way"...feel free to skip it.
summary: Mel and Goldie at their best!
